    public static final class Replicator.ModifyFailure<A extends ReplicatedData>
extends Replicator.UpdateFailure<A>
implements scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    If the modify function of the Replicator.Update throws an exception the reply message will be this ModifyFailure message. The original exception is included as cause.
